<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4126.3.5>
    bibo:endPage "410" ;
    bibo:issue "3" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "397" ;
    bibo:volume "4126" ;
    dc:creator "Sychra, Oldrich; Kolencik, Stanislav; Palma, Ricardo L." ;
    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "Three new species of Myrsidea (Phthiraptera: Menoponidae) from New Zealand passerines (Aves: Passeriformes)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.255291>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.255292>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.255294> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.255291>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 13. Myrsidea novaeseelandiae n. sp.: 9, female. 10, male metasternal plate and sternites I – II. 11, female prosternal plate. Myrsidea hihi n. sp.: 12, female dorso-ventral view of mesothorax, metathorax and abdomen. 13, female prosternal plate. Scale bars = 0.5 mm (Figs 9, 12); 0.1 mm (Fig. 10); 0.05 mm (Figs 11, 13)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/255291/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.255292>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14 – 22. Myrsidea ivanliteraki n. sp.: 14, male ventral terminalia. 15, male genitalia. 16, male genital sac sclerites (two morphs). Myrsidea vincula: 17, male genitalia. 18, male genital sac sclerite. Myrsidea novaeseelandiae n. sp.: 19, male ventral terminalia. 20, male genitalia. 21, male genital sac sclerite (two views). Myrsidea hihi n. sp.: 22, male genitalia. Scale bars = 0.10 mm (Figs 14, 19, 20, 22), 0.05 mm (Figs 15 – 18, 21)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/255292/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.255294>
    dc:description "FIGURES 27 – 30. Habitus. Myrsidea novaeseelandiae n. sp.: 27, holotype female. 28, paratype male. Myrsidea hihi n. sp.: 29, holotype female. 30, paratype male. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/255294/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

